text: __NOTOC__ Location of Winn Parish in Louisiana This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in Winn Parish, Louisiana. This is intended to be a complete list of the properties on the National Register of Historic Places in Winn Parish, Louisiana, United States. The locations of National Register properties for which the latitude and longitude coordinates are included below, may be seen in a map. There are 5 properties listed on the National Register in the parish.
